Setting,Change To,Why?
PROJECT_NAME,"""Beauty Contest""",The title of your documentation.
OUTPUT_DIRECTORY,"""Docs""",Keeps files organized in a separate folder.
RECURSIVE,YES,Crucial! Searches inside your logic/ and utils/ subfolders.
EXTRACT_ALL,YES,"Documents everything, even if you forgot to add comments."
HAVE_DOT,YES,Required for the graphs/diagrams you wanted.
CALL_GRAPH,YES,Draws a diagram of which function calls which.
CALLER_GRAPH,YES,Draws the reverse (who calls this function?).
SOURCE_BROWSER,YES,"Adds a ""Go to source code"" button."
INLINE_SOURCES = YES
GENERATE_RTF,YES,Tells Doxygen to build a Word-compatible file.
RTF_OUTPUT,rtf,Sets the folder name (default is rtf).
COMPACT_RTF,YES,"Makes the document look cleaner and less ""spaced out."""
RTF_HYPERLINKS,YES,"Makes clickable links (e.g., clicking a function name jumps to it)."
DOXYFILE_ENCODING = UTF-8
OUTPUT_LANGUAGE = Bulgarian


for no dependecies graph 

INCLUDE_GRAPH = NO
INCLUDED_BY_GRAPH = NO
DIRECTORY_GRAPH = NO
COLLABORATION_GRAPH = NO